 <span data-ttu-id="594c5-102">裝飾項會自訂<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>繫結至<xref:System.Windows.UIElement>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-102">An adorner is a custom <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement> that is bound to a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="594c5-103">裝飾項會呈現在裝飾項層，也就是一律為裝飾項目或集合所裝飾項目; 最上方的呈現表面轉譯的裝飾項無關的轉譯<xref:System.Windows.UIElement>裝飾項繫結至。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-103">Adorners are rendered in an adorner layer, which is a rendering surface that is always on top of the adorned element or a collection of adorned elements; rendering of an adorner is independent from rendering of the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> that the adorner is bound to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="594c5-104">裝飾項的位置通常會相對於它繫結到的項目，並使用標準 2D 座標，原點位於裝飾項目的左上角。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-104">An adorner is typically positioned relative to the element to which it is bound, using the standard 2-D coordinate origin located at the upper-left of the adorned element.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="594c5-105">父代<xref:System.Windows.Documents.Adorner>是<xref:System.Windows.Documents.AdornerLayer>呈現<xref:System.Windows.Documents.Adorner>不所裝飾的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-105">The parent of an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Adorner> is the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.AdornerLayer> that renders the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Adorner>, not the element being adorned.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="594c5-106">放在裝飾項圖層中的任何項目會轉譯在您已設定的其餘任何樣式之上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-106">Anything placed in the adorner layer is rendered on top of the rest of any styles you have set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="594c5-107">換句話說，裝飾項永遠是以視覺化方式在最上面，而且無法使用疊置順序覆寫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="594c5-107">In other words, adorners are always visually on top and cannot be overridden using z-order.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
